StyleHTML.headerMain: width: 95%; margin: 10px auto; text-align: center; font-size: 200%; font-weight: bold; color: #55F; background: #202020; border: 4px solid #181818; border-radius: 10px; user-select: none
StyleHTML.headerVeryBig: margin: 10px auto; text-align: center; font-size: 175%; font-weight: bold; color: #55F; user-select: none
StyleHTML.headerBig: margin: 10px auto; text-align: center; font-size: 150%; font-weight: bold; color: #55F; user-select: none
StyleHTML.headerMedium: margin: 10px auto; text-align: center; font-size: 125%; font-weight: bold; color: #55F; user-select: none
StyleHTML.headerSmall: margin: 10px auto; text-align: center; font-size: 100%; font-weight: bold; color: #55F; user-select: none
StyleHTML.headerVerySmall: margin: 10px auto; text-align: center; font-size: 75%; font-weight: bold; color: #55F; user-select: none
StyleHTML.textVeryBig: margin: 10px auto; text-align: center; font-size: 175%; color: #55F
StyleHTML.textBig: margin: 10px auto; text-align: center; font-size: 150%; color: #55F
StyleHTML.textMedium: margin: 10px auto; text-align: center; font-size: 125%; color: #55F
StyleHTML.textSmall: margin: 10px auto; text-align: center; font-size: 100%; color: #55F
StyleHTML.textVerySmall: margin: 10px auto; text-align: center; font-size: 75%; color: #55F
StyleHTML.buttonBig: z-index: 100; padding: 1px 8px 3px 8px; margin: 3px; text-align: center; font-size: 125%; word-wrap: break-word; color: #BFF; background: #333; border: 2px solid #55F; border-radius: 4px
StyleHTML.buttonMedium: z-index: 100; padding: 1px 6px 3px 6px; margin: 3px; text-align: center; font-size: 100%; word-wrap: break-word; color: #BFF; background: #333; border: 2px solid #55F; border-radius: 4px
StyleHTML.buttonSmall: z-index: 100; padding: 1px 4px 3px 4px; margin: 3px; text-align: center; font-size: 70%; word-wrap: break-word; color: #BFF; background: #333; border: 2px solid #55F; border-radius: 4px
StyleHTML.buttonImg: z-index: 100; padding: 4px; color: #55F; background: #222; border: 2px solid #222; border-radius: 8px; user-select: none
StyleHTML.inputBig: z-index: 110; padding: 1px 10px; margin: 3px; color: #BFF; font-size: 125%; background: #333; border: 2px solid #55F; border-radius: 6px; outline: none
StyleHTML.inputMedium: z-index: 110; padding: 1px 10px; margin: 3px; color: #BFF; font-size: 100%; background: #333; border: 2px solid #55F; border-radius: 6px; outline: none
StyleHTML.inputSmall: z-index: 110; padding: 1px 10px; margin: 3px; color: #BFF; font-size: 75%; background: #333; border: 2px solid #55F; border-radius: 6px; outline: none
StyleHTML.inputRange: z-index: 110; padding: 5px 10px; margin: 3px; accent-color: #F7E163; background: #333; border: 0px solid #55F; border-radius: 6px; outline: none
StyleHTML.inputDark: z-index: 110; padding: 5px 10px; background: #333; color: #F7E163; border: 0px; border-radius: 10px; outline: none
StyleHTML.selectMedium: z-index: 120; padding: 0px; margin: 3px; color: #BFF; font-size: 100%; background: #333; border: 2px solid #55F; border-radius: 4px; outline: none; overflow-y: hidden; scrollbar-width: none
StyleHTML.selectSmall: z-index: 120; padding: 0px; margin: 3px; color: #BFF; font-size: 75%; background: #333; border: 2px solid #55F; border-radius: 4px; outline: none; overflow-y: hidden; scrollbar-width: none
StyleHTML.divAlt: background: #55F; color: #111; padding: 5px; margin: 15px auto; border-radius: 10px
StyleHTML.divDark: background: #111; color: #F7E163; padding: 5px; margin: 15px auto; border: 4px solid #000; border-radius: 10px
StyleHTML.pageLinks_Base: width: 95%; color: #55F; margin-bottom: 0px; transition: opacity 0.25s, border-bottom 0.1s; border-radius: 6px; border-right: 4px solid #111; border-left: 4px solid #111

StyleCSS.selectHover: z-index: 121; margin-bottom: -100px; min-height: 100px; color: #FFF; background: #444; overflow-y: scroll; scrollbar-width: auto; transition: 0.25s
StyleCSS.selectFocus: z-index: 122; margin-bottom: -100px; min-height: 100px; color: #FFF; background: #444; overflow-y: scroll; scrollbar-width: auto; transition: 0.1s
StyleCSS.imgHover: z-index: 101; color: #FFF; background: #444; border: 3px solid #FBDF56; transition: 0.25s
StyleCSS.imgClick: z-index: 102; color: #55F; background: #550; border: 3px solid #FBDF56; transition: 0.1s
